@DATABASE "Bomb Jack"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Bomb Jack"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                                 Bomb Jack
                                 =========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49984,0)"}          49984,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49530,0)"}          49530,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

@endnode
